Integration Testing Plan

The purpose of integration testing is to confirm that different components of the system work together correctly.

Test Case 1: Add Patient + Schedule Appointment
  Add a new patient
  Schedule an appointment for that patient
  Expected Result: Patient appears in scheduling and appointment is created

Test Case 2: Data Storage
  Add patient and appointment
  Refresh page
  Expected Result: Data remains available using local storage

Test Case 3: View Appointments
  Schedule multiple appointments
  Expected Result: All appointments display correctly
